---
title: Falafel & Spiced Roast Veggie Couscous with Mint Yoghurt
description: What's a quick and easy way to bring a new burst of life to a dish? Add a fresh squeeze of lemon juice and colourful roasted veggies to couscous; it adds an extra hit of flavour with every bite! Teamed with warm falafel bites and mint yoghurt, this dish is all kinds of yum.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/falafel-lemony-couscous-5d73dfeb.jpg
